Permutate(String) - Constructor for class DogPoundBreakout.Permutate
Supply the string and this constructor will build a vector containing all the permutations of the string
permutateParts(char[], char[]) - Method in class DogPoundBreakout.Permutate
Recursively find the unique string patterns and rotate each of them
for example: "123" is 1(23) which is a unique pattern of 123.
and 1(32) is a unique pattern of 132.
position - Variable in class DogPoundBreakout.Permutate
